<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }
        .brand-image {
            height: 4rem;
            width: 4rem;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #3a003d;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        .welcome {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #3a003d;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
            color: #999999;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="brand-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/debwkutxb/image/upload/v1722239665/my-ecom/ah30cob3jtnspais47yp.png" alt="brand-image">
            <h1>Subscription Confirmation</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome">Welcome to My Ecom Newsletter!</div>
            <p>Thank you for subscribing to our newsletter. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
            <p>You will now receive regular updates about our latest products, special offers, and exclusive content directly to your inbox.</p>
            <p>We hope you enjoy our updates, and if you ever wish to unsubscribe, you can do so easily by clicking the unsubscribe link in any of our emails.</p>
            <p>Thank you for joining our community!</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>My Ecom Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you did not subscribe to this newsletter, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
